    titleEn: "The Ten Qira'at: Understanding Different Quran Readings",
    titleAr: "القراءات العشر: فهم القراءات المختلفة للقرآن",
    excerptEn: "There are ten authentic ways to recite the Quran. Learn about the Qira'at and their significance.",
